org.cloudgraph.hbase.filter

Class GraphFetchColumnFilterAssembler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.hbase.filter.FilterListAssembler
      • org.cloudgraph.hbase.filter.GraphFetchColumnFilterAssembler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assembler, HBaseFilterAssembler

    public class GraphFetchColumnFilterAssembler
extends FilterListAssembler
implements HBaseFilterAssembler
    Creates an HBase column filter set based on the given criteria which leverages the HBase MultipleColumnPrefixFilter to return only columns which make up the selected data graph. The advantage of this strategy is that a complete graph of any complexity may be returned in a single round trip.
    Since:
    0.5
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
    See Also:
    GraphColumnKeyFactory, InitialFetchColumnFilterAssembler
